title: Forest Shooting Ranger [Arcade, Eng, 2018]
description:
FOREST SHOOTING RANGER - arcade shooter, one target at a time

Moving through the woods you have to hit as many targets as possible.
For every successful shot you are awarded bonus points.
Hit a moving target to earn extra points.
Try to choose goals that are designated as priorities (silhouetted in the top of the screen).
For these, you will earn the most points and bonuses (extra time and the number of rounds).
The residence time in the dash is limited.
Movement - "up" - "down" keys. Shooting - left mouse button.
Pause Exit menu - Esc.
Change some of the parameters of the game and you will be able to file cfg.txt

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 1 GHz
RAM: 128 mb
VRAM: 64 mb
HDD: 42 mb
